<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Arimo:ital,wght@0,400..700;1,400..700&family=Bangers&family=Patrick+Hand&family=Quicksand:wght@300..700&family=Roboto+Mono:ital,wght@0,100..700;1,100..700&family=Special+Elite&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/index.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/0580340085.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>FurFriends</title>
  </head> 
  <body>
    <header>
      <%- include('modules/navbar.ejs')%>
    </header>
    <div class="bg1 p-4">
      <div class="container-fluid text-white">
        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center" style="margin-block: 1rem;">
          <div class="col-xl-9 p-3">
            <p class="text-center fs-4 p-5" style="color: #37260c;">"The idea for this social network was born out of the unconditional love we share with our pets. We wanted a unique space where owners and their animals could take center stage—a place to share special moments, connect with fellow animal lovers, and celebrate the joy they bring to our lives every day. Here, every bark, purr, and leap tells a story. We created this community so you and your furry companion can find friends, share experiences, and, most importantly, feel at home. Welcome to our pet-loving family. Welcome to FurFriends!"</p>
          </div>
        </div> 
      </div>
      <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center" style="margin-block: 1rem;">
        <% result.forEach((elem) => { %>
          <div class="col-xl-2 p-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
            <a href="/user/oneUser/<%= elem.user_id %>"><img class="imghover" src="/images/user/<%= elem.user_img ? elem.user_img:'user-default.jpg' %>" style="width: 200px; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%;" alt=""></a>
          </div>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-5"><a class="nav-link fw-bold fs-6 meetbutton" style="border: 2px solid #37260c; border-radius: 20px; margin-inline: 1rem; padding: 1rem;" href="/user/allUsers">Meet them</a></div>
      <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center row-gap-4" style="margin-block: 1rem;">
        <div class="col-xl-6  col-12 p-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
          <img class="imghover" src="/images/assets/about.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 300px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%;" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-6 col-12 p-4 d-flex justify-content-center flex-column align-items-center text-center">
          <span class="fw-bold fs-5">"Faith on the Trail"</span>
          <p>Adopting Faith, my rescue dog, changed everything. Weekend hikes to tire her out turned into shared adventures that I began posting online. Her joy resonated, and strangers told me our photos inspired them to explore too. Now, every trail we conquer isn’t just for us—it’s to remind others to find their own moments of peace. Faith taught me that sometimes, a single post can spark countless journeys. 🌲🐾</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-6 col-12 p-4 d-flex justify-content-center flex-column align-items-center text-center">
          <span class="fw-bold fs-5">"Miles of Connection"</span>
          <p>I never thought a simple ride with Thunder would mean so much. One day, I shared a photo of us with the mountain in the distance, and it took off online. People commented about dreams of freedom, of reconnecting with nature. Now, every ride feels bigger than me—it’s about reminding others that sometimes the best path forward is through the wild. Thunder and I just share the view. 🌄🐎 #RideYourJourney</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-6 col-12 p-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
          <img class="imghover" src="/images/assets/about1.jpeg" style="width: 300px; height: 300px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%;" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-6 col-12 p-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
          <img class="imghover" src="/images/assets/about2.webp" style="width: 300px; height: 300px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%;" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-6 col-12 p-4 d-flex justify-content-center flex-column align-items-center text-center">
          <span class="fw-bold fs-5">"Hiking Partners for Life"</span>
          <p>When Max got tired halfway up the trail, I didn’t hesitate—I tucked him into my backpack and kept climbing. I snapped a quick photo, and to my surprise, it went viral. People loved seeing our bond and shared stories of their own adventures. Now, every hike feels like more than a journey—it’s a reminder to carry those we love, no matter how steep the climb. 🏞️🐕 #TrailTales</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-6 col-12 p-4 d-flex justify-content-center flex-column align-items-center text-center">
          <span class="fw-bold fs-5">"All You Need is Cat"</span>
          <p>It started as a joke—Leo sprawled out next to the sign, perfectly unbothered. I snapped a picture and shared it online, not expecting much. The response was overwhelming: comments, likes, and shares from cat lovers everywhere. Now, Leo’s chill vibes remind people daily that the simplest things—like a catnap—can bring the most joy. 🐾💛 #AllYouNeedIsCat</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-6 col-12 p-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
          <img class="imghover" src="/images/assets/about3.jpeg" style="width: 300px; height: 300px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%;" alt="">
        </div>
      </div> 
    </div>
    <%- include('modules/footer.ejs') %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </body>
</html>
